  "intent_precise": "0479ad.ot2.apiv2: Using reagent_plate (labware, slot Reagent Plate at 4 Degrees C), output_plate (labware, slot Output Plate at 4 Degrees C), mag_plate (labware, slot Magnetic Module Plate - 300 uL PCR Plate + Adapter), Reagent Reservoir (reservoir, slot 2). With Temperature Module module, Temperature Module module, magnetic module. (1) Wait 10 seconds. (2) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (3) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (4) Disengage magnets to release beads. (5) Pause: format (6) Transfer 80\u00b5L from source to destination. (7) Pause: \nRemove magnetic module plate for off-deck incubation\n    (65 degrees 5 min, cool to 4 degrees C). Return and resume.\n (8) Transfer 80\u00b5L from source to destination. (9) Incubate for 5 minutes. (10) Engage magnets at height_engagemm height for bead separation. (11) Pause for incubation. (12) Transfer 75\u00b5L from source to destination. (13) Wait 1 seconds. (14) Disengage magnets to release beads. (15) Transfer 180\u00b5L from source to destination. (16) Wait 1 seconds. (17) Transfer 144\u00b5L from source to destination. (18) Engage magnets at height_engagemm height for bead separation. (19) Pause for incubation. (20) Wait 0 seconds. (21) Disengage magnets to release beads. (22) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination. (23) Transfer 43\u00b5L from source to destination. (24) Pause: \nRemove magnetic module plate for off-deck incubation\n    (lid 90, 80 degrees 2 min, cool to 25 degrees C). Return and resume.\n (25) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination. (26) Transfer 80\u00b5L from source to destination. (27) Wait 1 seconds. (28) Incubate for 5 minutes. (29) Engage magnets at height_engagemm height for bead separation. (30) Pause for incubation. (31) Transfer 75\u00b5L from source to destination. (32) Wait 1 seconds. (33) Disengage magnets to release beads. (34) Transfer 180\u00b5L from source to destination. (35) Transfer 144\u00b5L from source to destination. (36) Engage magnets at height_