  "intent_concise": "Perform magnetic bead separation, temperature control (4\u00b0C). (volumes 10\u00b5L-200\u00b5L, ~15 min total)",
  "intent": "For this magnetic bead-based protocol, start by cooling both temperature modules to 4\u00b0C and wait 10 seconds before disengaging the magnets to release the beads. You'll be doing several rounds of transfers and magnetic separations - first transfer 80\u00b5L, then remove the magnetic plate for a 5-minute incubation at 65\u00b0C before cooling to 4\u00b0C, followed by another 80\u00b5L transfer and 5-minute on-deck incubation. The protocol involves multiple magnetic separations with transfers of 75\u00b5L, 180\u00b5L, and 144\u00b5L, then smaller volumes of 50\u00b5L and 43\u00b5L, with two more off-deck incubations (80\u00b0C for 2 minutes, then 94\u00b0C for 15 minutes with immediate cooling on ice once it reaches 65\u00b0C), finishing with a final 2-minute magnetic separation and 10\u00b5L transfer from source A1 to column 2.",
